{"tid":2290664,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共想係委任立法會會期內處理引入中國醫護","createTime":"2020-11-18T07:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T09:49:25.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"965308fd617e93edc61c89eb71078a3c65986bf6","tid":2290664,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:23:32.000Z","msg":"延任立法會大會周三（18日）將續會，辯論一項有關制訂輸入非本地培訓醫生的新機制的議案。香港醫護界質疑新機制議案的實質需要，指現時已有機制讓非本地培訓醫生在港執業。<br />\n<br />\n該項議案由身兼行政會議成員的飲食界議員張宇人提出。他在議案中指出，「要求政府盡快制訂新機制，輸入有經驗及有質素的非本地培訓醫生，以紓緩公營醫療系統醫生不足的情況，並有效回應本港人口老化所引致的醫療服務需求。」"},{"pid":"0b01317fa2e8a77ba82c34457dee9ef22098ac3d","tid":2290664,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:31:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb680bdfe1ecac290562e1570d1e3f6effa3030","tid":2290664,"uid":886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:32:23.000Z","msg":"已經好多大陸醫生啦，做野又閪又求其，仲大把女食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144f2a194d242208ea145d4b93add9687d9bdf43","tid":2290664,"uid":128417,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"張宇人你連自己飲食界都未搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走去搞醫護界"},{"pid":"4b88edcb3da4b2f493c13174018ab5d84eb617d6","tid":2290664,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9481ad74d68107eed283271dd78736e80e180600","tid":2290664,"uid":51840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:36:38.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\n之後就算有選舉<br />\n你覺得會有分别"},{"pid":"fa2af9d94366313a01db0dbd441d88d9497861e6","tid":2290664,"uid":45376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:36:44.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\n反正連登仔最鍾意屌醫護霸權<br />\n又鍾意屌人罷工冇料到抵撚死<br />\n而家未幾好可以一齊享受做支那人榮耀準備定「紅包」啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fddf34f09f992ed8e1b7b9e19c350ec5c1f6c01","tid":2290664,"uid":28528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"144f2a194d242208ea145d4b93add9687d9bdf43","tid":2290664,"uid":128417,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"張宇人你連自己飲食界都未搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走去搞醫護界"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:04:08.000Z","msg":"張宇人稱女婿未能回港執業 批醫學界「刻薄同業」<br />\n張宇人今日出席一個電台節目時表示，他的女兒和女婿現時在美國的公立醫院任職專科醫生，女婿原在數年前計劃回港執業，但因本港未有放寬海外醫生回港執業的制度，令他打消念頭。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190413/OWPPNP2TBNJXEWPI34GNFAMPRE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190413%2FOWPPNP2TBNJXEWPI34GNFAMPRE%2F&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1eSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=4fe937e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190413%2FOWPPNP2TBNJXEWPI34GNFAMPRE%2F&h=5998196f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20190413/OWPPNP2TBNJXEWPI34GNFAMPRE/</a><br />\n根據佢都係為左自己友去爭取，但唔知會唔會變左做第二樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3307254bd67d70824df6b91f5433b1a402d16c35","tid":2290664,"uid":79410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:07:05.000Z","msg":"仆街就仆街在, 中國醫護取代香港醫護, 對仆街跟本冇影響. <br />\n呢班撚樣, 有錢都係睇返香港私家醫生. <br />\n或者好似譚耀宗咁, 指定公立醫生, 仲有得打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9626ac501533e81af34da0491780cdb46b523a58","tid":2290664,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:24:26.000Z","msg":"制裁咗佢個女同女婿先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9621af0bae52da2b03e8807fa512dabb684cbea9","tid":2290664,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"到時死多咗人點算"},{"pid":"b0cf702cd3355d6f2a698c6c66fa93abe1b51763","tid":2290664,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9621af0bae52da2b03e8807fa512dabb684cbea9","tid":2290664,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"到時死多咗人點算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"支那處理方法 搵D理由解釋死因<br />\n家屬追究就拉家屬"},{"pid":"9244cf2a23ce24084745736c88b2b24c35b6606e","tid":2290664,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:46:36.000Z","msg":"點解唔係資助香港人北上求醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c1c8b9a06f498d4fb25d980bd9c4a234c7f419","tid":2290664,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:49:25.000Z","msg":"求撚其啦<br />\n反正連登仔唔去睇公立"}]}